<p>Several libraries are built upon the Decentraland SDK to help you build faster:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/decentraland-ecs-utils">Utils library</a>: Simplifies a lot of common tasks like moving or rotating an entity, or triggering a function when the player walks into a cube.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://www.decentral.io/docs/dcl/overview/">Decentral API</a>: Simplifies making fast and cheap blockchain transactions triggered by the scene, using the Matic network.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

